commit.message: Run precommit on changed files from parent
add User-Agent to linode salt-cloud module
Use salt.utils to get bower path

Merge pull request #49901 from twangboy/fix_startup_issues

Fix issues with startup in Windows
On start, update git_pillar on first loop, withour waiting git_pillar_update_interval
Added device validation before executing mkpart

Re-added mkpartfs to not break compatibility

- Re-added mkpartfs to not break compatibility, now it only calls
  mkpart.
- Added a new unit test to make sure that mkpartfs is still there
  and all arguments are passed to mkpart

Added mkpart unit tests and removed mkpartfs

- Removed mkpartfs as it is the same of mkpart. No code inside Salt
  uses mkpartfs.
- Moved the last change "if fs_type and not _is_fstype(fs_type)" to
  mkpart.
- Added tests to check if mkpart allows the creation of a partition
  with no fstype specified.

Fixed Bug LVM has no Parttion Type.

        cmd = ('parted', '-m', '-s', '--', device, 'mkpart', part_type, fs_type, start, end)
